      "endSec": 4.785,
      "kind": "selling",
      "clip": "mx_zhuanxing/s1.mp4",
      "feature": "people",
      "hl": []
    },
    {
      "text": "不是华人不会做生意,是纯靠低价杂货走量这套,利润越摊越薄。",
      "startSec": 4.905,
      "endSec": 10.383,
      "kind": "selling",
      "clip": "mx_zhuanxing/s2.mp4",
      "feature": "wall",
      "hl": []
    },
    {
      "text": "活下来、做大的,几乎都在干同一件事:往超市、专业店转,品类往上做。",
      "startSec": 10.503,
      "endSec": 16.77,
      "kind": "selling",
      "clip": "mx_zhuanxing/s3.mp4",
      "feature": "aisle",
      "hl": []
    },
    {
      "text": "可转型最大的坎是货源:专业品类,本地批发根本配不齐。",
      "startSec": 16.89,
      "endSec": 21.627,
      "kind": "selling",
      "clip": "mx_zhuanxing/s4.mp4",
      "feature": "loading",
      "hl": []
    },
    {
      "text": "家居、家电、五金、汽车用品想一站备齐,你得到处找供应商,累还凑不全。",
      "startSec": 21.747,
      "endSec": 28.23,
